        <span>Type set in GT America by <a href="https://www.grillitype.com/typeface/gt-america" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Grilli Type</a> Foundry.</span>
        <em>This website is not indexed, and uses no trackers or analytics.</em></footer>
    </div>
</div>
<main role="main" class="blog-content">
<h1 class="page-title-responsive"><a href="{{ '/' | url }}">{{ meta.title }}</a></h1>
    {{ content | safe }}
</main>
</div>
</body>
</html>
